# Power BI Report Factory

## What to Ignore

# MCP server source (cloned by setup script, not part of this repo)
.mcp-servers/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editor files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/

# Node (if MCP servers are installed locally)
node_modules/

# Power BI temporary files
*.pbix
*.pbit
~$*

# Keep .pbip files (they're text-based and version-controlled)
# But ignore any auto-generated temp files
*.tmp
